modules.description: This module offers efficient text manipulation through a rope-based structure, enabling operations like insertion, deletion, substring extraction, and line-based navigation alongside advanced features such as encoding-aware indexing, pattern matching, and transactional undo/redo. It works with rope instances and strings, supporting history tracking, file serialization, and customizable traversal patterns for text analysis or transformation. Designed for applications requiring scalable text editing, persistent state management, and performance-critical tasks like real-time collaboration or large document processing.
